law.catch_line: Commissioner to enforce KRS 304.17A-500 to 304.17A-570 -- Administrative regulations.
law.text: The commissioner shall enforce the provisions of KRS 304.17A-500 to 304.17A-570 and shall adopt administrative regulations necessary to carry out the provisions of KRS 304.17A-500 to 304.17A-570.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1234, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 496, sec. 38, effective April 10, 1998.
